name: Luck
description: Behold the radiant four-leaf clover, not merely a symbol, but a powerful conduit of boundless, untamed luck. This rare, emerald charm pulsates with an energy strong enough to shatter the most intricately rigged systems and expose every hidden manipulation. Wield its fortune to turn the tides decisively, making every deceitful developer regret their ill-gotten gains. Spread its incredible, far-reaching influence to level the playing field, ensuring that those who've been unfairly targeted or suppressed by crooked schemes receive their rightful share of prosperity and success. Justice will bloom, and the seeds of true luck will finally flourish for all.
